reviews.text:
Spacious seating, good service, decent food.
Some patrons may find certain dishes slightly pricey, if you choose carefully, you can get a balanced meal at good value. 
I ordered scallops and Sakura shrimp salad and deep-fried chicken with Sakura shrimps.
Portions were good - 3 big scallops on a mountain of veggies. 
The chicken pieces were piping hot, crunchy and not greasy at all.
Overpriced and food quality is so-so
Ok for a quick bite, a bit pricy.
Popular for me lately being a westerner.. I love my salads. This place has a few salads on offer, pizzas and pastas. Great taste. Just make sure you have cash on you. No octopus pay or EPS..

Overpriced food, the pizza was fast food style and actually lukewarm after being served. They don't serve real Italian pizza. The pizza base is too thin, and the pizza is too small. The salad was ok. Staff were impersonal, taciturn and reserved. - There are definitely better alternatives at City One for pizza.

reviews.text: 西式餐廳，價錢中高，食物份量大份

Spacious seating, good service, decent food.
Some patrons may find certain dishes slightly pricey, if you choose carefully, you can get a balanced meal at good value. 
I ordered scallops and Sakura shrimp salad and deep-fried chicken with Sakura shrimps.
Portions were good - 3 big scallops on a mountain of veggies. 
The chicken pieces were piping hot, crunchy and not greasy at all.
雖在商場內，環境尚可接受，下午茶時間套餐選擇不太少、頗夠份量；焦糖咖啡相當不俗，不太甜。
Overpriced and food quality is so-so
在這間意大利Tomato Cafe'用餐感到好舒適，清靜優雅，服務佳。能提供美味pizza、沙律、意粉，特色蛋糕(如芝士蛋糕)，還有焦糖咖啡。座位室內室外都有，值得去試試。開放時間:由週日-六，11:00-23:00。

reviews.text:
It's a neighborhood mall. Has shops supply to the needs of the residents of Cityone. There's a MacD, Starbucks, Manning's, Watson's, and numerous restaurants. Nothing fancy. 

The one shop worth mentioning though, is the Adidas Outlet. This shop has a good selection of the previous season's collection at bargain prices. Just this shop alone is worth visiting this mall.
Not a big shopping centre. Nevertheless, some eateries still attract students and visitors.
A good mall with a good balance between fashion and other stuff for people who don't buy clothing every day.
Good.👍
A good place for the local community with real products useful for the locals.

reviews.text:
It's a neighborhood mall. Has shops supply to the needs of the residents of Cityone. There's a MacD, Starbucks, Manning's, Watson's, and numerous restaurants. Nothing fancy. 

The one shop worth mentioning though, is the Adidas Outlet. This shop has a good selection of the previous season's collection at bargain prices. Just this shop alone is worth visiting this mall.
商場店舖種類各式各樣，尤其食館特別多！
沒有泊車優惠，可以不去。

為沙田最大型私人屋苑，"致富"與 "置富" 同音因而得名。第一城的交通真是方便。城內有兩個商塲; 置富第一城，及在銀城街的置富第一城.樂薈。置富第一城的商場有兩層，面積較大、樂薈商塲是地下那層，樓上是停車場。兩面商塲都夠光猛，食物店多元化，中西都有。置富第一城中心有一個廣場，也稱置富第一"園"，每當節日期間，"園"內就舉辦嘉年華活動(如中秋嘉年華、聖誕節)，共賀中秋，為第一城居民帶來節日氣氛、家家共享、快樂年年。
